(3332,	1,	'2016-01-13 14:33:40',	'2016-01-13 14:33:40',	'<ul class=\"sow-slider-images\">		<li class=\"sow-slider-image sow-slider-image-cover\" style=\"background-color: #333333\">\r\n<h1>So you\'re building a website that might not be written in English?</h1><h3>No problem, Hestia Pro has you covered.</h3>			\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>				<ol class=\"sow-slider-pagination\">\r\n<li><a href=\"#\">1</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<em class=\"sow-sld-icon-thin-right\"></em>\r\n</a>\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<em class=\"sow-sld-icon-thin-left\"></em>\r\n</a>\r\n<p>The code of this theme has been written <strong>with localization in mind.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This means that you can create the default language files that WordPress uses (<em>.po</em> and <em>.mo</em>) and translate every text displayed by the theme without getting your hands dirty in the source code.</p>\r\n<p>[su_note note_color=\"#f1f1f1\"]By the way, we\'ll be happy to provide you with a handy guide on how to get this done. Really, no particular expertise needed ... other than knowing how to say certain things in your target language, of course. ;)[/su_note]</p>\r\n<p>[su_frame align=\"center\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-3349 aligncenter\" src=\"https://demo.themeisle.com/zerif-pro/wp-content/uploads/sites/68/2016/01/language-files.gif\" alt=\"language-files\" width=\"301\" height=\"324\">[/su_frame]</p>\r\n<h3>But let\'s take it even further</h3>\r\n<h2>Introducing RTL text (right-to-left)</h2>\r\n<p>Maybe you\'re working on a site in Hebrew, or Arabic, or any other RTL language.</p>\r\n<p>With this new version of Zerif Pro this is no issue. Just switch the language, and the theme will follow suit by changing the default display mode to RTL.</p>\r\n<p>Quick example:</p>\r\n<p>[su_frame align=\"center\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3346\" src=\"https://demo.themeisle.com/zerif-pro/wp-content/uploads/sites/68/2016/01/rtl-demo.jpg\" alt=\"rtl-demo\" width=\"800\">[/su_frame]</p>',	'Translation &amp; RTL Ready',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'translation-rtl-ready',	'',	'',	'2017-06-23 12:23:16',	'2017-06-23 12:23:16',	'',	0,	'https://demo.themeisle.com/parallax-one-staging/?page_id=3332',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
